      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've heard from people that a tiny bit of wine actually helps people with anxiety relax better with their meds. like, if i just have like half a glass, it won't really be a big deal right? i'm not looking to get drunk, just want to make sure it doesn't mess up the sleepiness part.",
